doc:
Transforms the `Option<T>` into a [`Result<T, E>`], mapping [`Some(v)`] to
[`Ok(v)`] and [`None`] to [`Err(err())`].

[`Ok(v)`]: Ok
[`Err(err())`]: Err
[`Some(v)`]: Some

# Examples

```
let x = Some("foo");
assert_eq!(x.ok_or_else(|| 0), Ok("foo"));

let x: Option<&str> = None;
assert_eq!(x.ok_or_else(|| 0), Err(0));
```
